{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Hi there. I'm Hasan. I'm an artist."},{"time":2000,"text":"And usually when I tell people I'm an artist,"},{"time":5000,"text":"they just look at me and say, \"Do you paint?\""},{"time":7000,"text":"or \"What kind of medium do you work in?\""},{"time":10000,"text":"Well most of my work that I work with"},{"time":12000,"text":"is really a little bit about methodologies of working"},{"time":15000,"text":"rather than actually a specific discipline"},{"time":18000,"text":"or a specific technique."},{"time":20000,"text":"So what I'm really interested in is creative problem solving."},{"time":23000,"text":"And I had a little bit of a problem a few years ago."},{"time":26000,"text":"So let me show you a little of that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"So it started over here."},{"time":30000,"text":"And this is the Detroit airport in June 19th of 2002."},{"time":34000,"text":"I was flying back to the U.S. from an exhibition overseas."},{"time":37000,"text":"And as I was coming back,"},{"time":39000,"text":"well I was taken by the FBI, met by an FBI agent,"},{"time":42000,"text":"and went into a little room"},{"time":44000,"text":"and he asked me all sorts of questions --"},{"time":46000,"text":"\"Where were you? What were you doing? Who were you talking with?"},{"time":48000,"text":"Why were you there? Who pays for your trips?\" --"},{"time":50000,"text":"all these little details."},{"time":52000,"text":"And then literally just out of nowhere,"},{"time":54000,"text":"the guy asks me, \"Where were you September 12th?\""},{"time":57000,"text":"And when most of us get asked, \"Where were you September 12th?\""},{"time":59000,"text":"or any date for that fact,"},{"time":61000,"text":"it's like, \"I don't exactly remember, but I can look it up for you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":64000,"text":"So I pulled out my little PDA,"},{"time":66000,"text":"and I said, \"Okay, let's look up my appointments for September 12th.\""},{"time":69000,"text":"I had September 12th -- from 10:00 a.m. to 10:30 a.m., I paid my storage bill."},{"time":72000,"text":"From 10:30 a.m. to 12:00 p.m., I met with Judith who was one of my graduate students at the time."},{"time":75000,"text":"From 12:00 p.m. to 3:00 p.m., I taught my intro class,"},{"time":77000,"text":"3:00 p.m. to 6:00 p.m., I taught my advanced class."},{"time":79000,"text":"\"Where were you the 11th?\" \"Where were you the 10th?\""},{"time":81000,"text":"\"Where were you the 29th? the 30th?\""},{"time":83000,"text":"\"Where were you October 5th?\""},{"time":85000,"text":"We read about six months of my calendar."},{"time":88000,"text":"And I don't think he was expecting me to have such detailed records"},{"time":91000,"text":"of what I did."},{"time":93000,"text":"But good thing I did,"},{"time":95000,"text":"because I don't look good in orange."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"So he asked me --"},{"time":101000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":103000,"text":"\"So this storage unit that you paid the rent on,"},{"time":105000,"text":"what did you have in it?\""},{"time":108000,"text":"This was in Tampa, Florida,"},{"time":110000,"text":"so I was like, \"Winter clothes that I have no use for in Florida."},{"time":113000,"text":"Furniture that I can't fit in my ratty apartment."},{"time":116000,"text":"Just assorted garage sale junk,"},{"time":119000,"text":"because I'm a pack rat.\""},{"time":121000,"text":"And he looks at me really confused and says, \"No explosives?\""},{"time":124000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":126000,"text":"I was like, \"No, no. I'm pretty certain there were no explosives."},{"time":128000,"text":"And if there were, I would have remembered that one.\""},{"time":131000,"text":"And he's still a little confused,"},{"time":133000,"text":"but I think that anyone who talks to me for more than a couple of minutes"},{"time":135000,"text":"realizes I'm not exactly a terrorist threat."},{"time":138000,"text":"And so we're sitting there,"},{"time":141000,"text":"and eventually after about an hour, hour and a half of just going back and forth,"},{"time":145000,"text":"he says, \"Okay, I have enough information here."},{"time":147000,"text":"I'm going to pass this onto the Tampa office. They're the ones who initiated this."},{"time":149000,"text":"They'll follow up with you, and we'll take care of it.\""},{"time":151000,"text":"I was like, \"Great.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":153000,"text":"So I got home and the phone rings,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and a man introduced himself."},{"time":158000,"text":"Basically this is the FBI offices in Tampa"},{"time":161000,"text":"where I spent six months of my life --"},{"time":163000,"text":"back and forth, not six months continuously."},{"time":165000,"text":"By the way, you folks know that in the United States,"},{"time":167000,"text":"you can't take photographs of federal buildings,"},{"time":169000,"text":"but Google can do it for you."},{"time":171000,"text":"So to the folks from Google, thank you."},{"time":173000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":176000,"text":"So I spent a lot of time in this building."},{"time":178000,"text":"Questions like:"},{"time":180000,"text":"\"Have you ever witnessed or participated in any act"},{"time":183000,"text":"that may be detrimental to the United States or a foreign nation?\""},{"time":187000,"text":"And you also have to consider the state of mind you're in"},{"time":189000,"text":"when you're doing this."},{"time":191000,"text":"You're basically face-to-face with someone"},{"time":193000,"text":"that essentially decides life or death."},{"time":196000,"text":"Or questions such as -- actually, during the polygraph,"},{"time":198000,"text":"which was how it finally ended after nine consecutive of them --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":201000,"text":"one of the polygraph questions was ..."},{"time":203000,"text":"well the first one was, \"Is your name Hasan?\" \"Yes.\""},{"time":206000,"text":"\"Are we in Florida?\" \"Yes.\" \"Is today Tuesday?\" \"Yes.\""},{"time":209000,"text":"Because you have to base it on a yes or no."},{"time":211000,"text":"Then, of course, the next question is:"},{"time":213000,"text":"\"Do you belong to any groups that wish to harm the United States?\""},{"time":216000,"text":"I work at a university."},{"time":218000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":220000,"text":"So I was like, \"Maybe you want to ask some of my colleagues that directly.\""},{"time":224000,"text":"But they said, \"Okay, aside from what we had discussed,"},{"time":227000,"text":"do you belong to any groups that wish to harm the United States?\""},{"time":229000,"text":"I was like, \"No.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"So at the end of six months of this"},{"time":233000,"text":"and nine consecutive polygraphs,"},{"time":235000,"text":"they said, \"Hey, everything's fine.\""},{"time":237000,"text":"I was like, \"I know. That's what I've been trying to tell you guys all along."},{"time":239000,"text":"I know everything's fine.\""},{"time":241000,"text":"So they're looking at me really odd."},{"time":244000,"text":"And it's like, \"Guys, I travel a lot.\""},{"time":246000,"text":"This is with the FBI."},{"time":248000,"text":"And I was like, \"All we need is Alaska not to get the last memo,"},{"time":250000,"text":"and here we go all over again.\""},{"time":252000,"text":"And there was a sincere concern there."},{"time":254000,"text":"And he was like, \"You know, if you get into trouble,"},{"time":256000,"text":"give us a call -- we'll take care of it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"So ever since then, before I would go anywhere, I would call the FBI."},{"time":261000,"text":"I would tell them, \"Hey guys, this is where I'm going. This is my flight."},{"time":264000,"text":"Northwest flight seven coming into Seattle"},{"time":267000,"text":"on March 12th\" or whatever."},{"time":269000,"text":"A couple weeks later, I'd call again, let them know."},{"time":271000,"text":"It wasn't that I had to, but I chose to."},{"time":274000,"text":"Just wanted to say, \"Hey guys."},{"time":276000,"text":"Don't want to make it look like I'm making any sudden moves.\""},{"time":278000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":280000,"text":"\"I don't want you guys to think that I'm about to flee."},{"time":283000,"text":"Just letting you know. Heads up.\""},{"time":285000,"text":"And so I just kept doing this over and over and over."},{"time":287000,"text":"And then the phone calls turned into emails,"},{"time":289000,"text":"and the emails got longer and longer and longer ..."},{"time":291000,"text":"with pictures,"},{"time":293000,"text":"with travel tips."},{"time":295000,"text":"Then I'd make websites."},{"time":297000,"text":"And then I built this over here. Let me go back to it over here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299000,"text":"So I actually designed this back in 2003."},{"time":302000,"text":"So this kind of tracks me at any given moment."},{"time":305000,"text":"I wrote some code for my mobile phone."},{"time":307000,"text":"Basically, what I decided is okay guys, you want to watch me, that's cool."},{"time":310000,"text":"But I'll watch myself. It's okay."},{"time":312000,"text":"You don't have to waste your energy or your resources."},{"time":314000,"text":"And I'll help you out."},{"time":317000,"text":"So in the process, I start thinking, well what else might they know about me?"},{"time":320000,"text":"Well they probably have all my flight records,"},{"time":322000,"text":"so I decided to put all my flight records from birth online."},{"time":327000,"text":"So you can see, Delta 1252"},{"time":330000,"text":"going from Kansas City to Atlanta."},{"time":332000,"text":"And then you see, these are some of the meals that I've been fed on the planes."},{"time":337000,"text":"This was on Delta 719"},{"time":339000,"text":"going from JFK to San Francisco."},{"time":343000,"text":"See that? They won't let me on a plane with that,"},{"time":346000,"text":"but they'll give it to me on the plane."},{"time":348000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":350000,"text":"These are the airports that I hang out in,"},{"time":352000,"text":"because I like airports."},{"time":354000,"text":"That's Kennedy airport, May 19th, Tuesday."},{"time":357000,"text":"This is in Warsaw."},{"time":360000,"text":"Singapore. You can see, they're kind of empty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363000,"text":"These images are shot really anonymously"},{"time":365000,"text":"to the point where it could be anyone."},{"time":367000,"text":"But if you can cross-reference this with the other data,"},{"time":370000,"text":"then you're basically replaying the roll of the FBI agent"},{"time":372000,"text":"and putting it all together."},{"time":374000,"text":"And when you're in a situation"},{"time":376000,"text":"where you have to justify every moment of your existence,"},{"time":378000,"text":"you're put in the situation where you react in a very different manner."},{"time":381000,"text":"At the time that this was going on,"},{"time":383000,"text":"the last thing on my mind was \"art project.\""},{"time":386000,"text":"I was certainly not thinking, hey, I got new work here."},{"time":389000,"text":"But after going through this, after realizing, well what just happened?"},{"time":392000,"text":"And after piecing together this, this and this,"},{"time":394000,"text":"this way of actually trying to figure out what happened for myself"},{"time":397000,"text":"eventually evolved into this,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and it actually became this project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":402000,"text":"So these are the stores that I shop in -- some of them --"},{"time":404000,"text":"because they need to know."},{"time":406000,"text":"This is me buying some duck flavored paste"},{"time":408000,"text":"at the Ranch 99 in Daly City"},{"time":410000,"text":"on Sunday, November 15th."},{"time":412000,"text":"At Coreana Supermarket"},{"time":414000,"text":"buying my kimchi because I like kimchi."},{"time":416000,"text":"And I bought some crabs too right around there,"},{"time":419000,"text":"and some chitlins at the Safeway in Emoryville."},{"time":422000,"text":"And laundry too. Laundry detergent at West Oakland --"},{"time":424000,"text":"East Oakland, sorry."},{"time":426000,"text":"And then my pickled jellyfish"},{"time":428000,"text":"at the Hong Kong Supermarket on Route 18 in East Brunswick."},{"time":431000,"text":"Now if you go to my bank records,"},{"time":433000,"text":"it'll actually show something from there,"},{"time":435000,"text":"so you know that, on May 9th,"},{"time":437000,"text":"that I bought $14.79 in fuel from Safeway Vallejo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440000,"text":"So not only that I'm giving this information here and there,"},{"time":444000,"text":"but now there's a third party,"},{"time":446000,"text":"an independent third party, my bank,"},{"time":449000,"text":"that's verifying that, yes indeed, I was there at this time."},{"time":451000,"text":"So there's points, and these points are actually being cross-referenced."},{"time":454000,"text":"And there's a verification taking place."},{"time":456000,"text":"Sometimes they're really small purchases."},{"time":458000,"text":"So 34 cents foreign transaction fee."},{"time":460000,"text":"All of these are extracted directly from my bank accounts,"},{"time":463000,"text":"and everything pops up right away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465000,"text":"Sometimes there's a lot of information."},{"time":467000,"text":"This is exactly where my old apartment in San Francisco was."},{"time":471000,"text":"And then sometimes you get this."},{"time":473000,"text":"Sometimes you just get this, just an empty hallway in Salt Lake City,"},{"time":475000,"text":"January 22nd."},{"time":477000,"text":"And I can tell you exactly who I was with, where I was,"},{"time":479000,"text":"because this is what I had to do with the FBI."},{"time":481000,"text":"I had to tell them every little detail of everything."},{"time":483000,"text":"I spend a lot of time on the road."},{"time":485000,"text":"This is a parking lot in Elko, Nevada"},{"time":487000,"text":"off of Route 80"},{"time":489000,"text":"at 8:01 p.m. on August 19th."},{"time":491000,"text":"I spend a lot of time in gas stations too -- empty train stations."},{"time":494000,"text":"So there's multiple databases."},{"time":496000,"text":"And there's thousands and thousands and thousands of images."},{"time":499000,"text":"There's actually 46,000 images right now on my site,"},{"time":502000,"text":"and the FBI has seen all of them --"},{"time":505000,"text":"at least I trust they've seen all of them."},{"time":508000,"text":"And then sometimes you don't get much information at all,"},{"time":511000,"text":"you just get this empty bed."},{"time":513000,"text":"And sometimes you get a lot of text information and no visual information."},{"time":516000,"text":"So you get something like this."},{"time":518000,"text":"This, by the way, is the location of my favorite sandwich shop in California --"},{"time":520000,"text":"Vietnamese sandwich."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522000,"text":"So there's different categorizations"},{"time":524000,"text":"of meals eaten outside"},{"time":526000,"text":"empty train stations, empty gas stations."},{"time":529000,"text":"These are some of the meals that I've been cooking at home."},{"time":531000,"text":"So how do you know these are meals eaten at home?"},{"time":533000,"text":"Well the same plate shows up a whole bunch of times."},{"time":536000,"text":"So again, you have to do some detective work here."},{"time":539000,"text":"So sometimes the databases get so specific."},{"time":542000,"text":"These are all tacos eaten in Mexico City"},{"time":544000,"text":"near a train station"},{"time":546000,"text":"on July fifth to July sixth."},{"time":549000,"text":"At 11:39 a.m. was this one."},{"time":551000,"text":"At 1:56 p.m. was this one. At 4:59 p.m. was this one."},{"time":554000,"text":"So I time-stamp my life every few moments."},{"time":557000,"text":"Every few moments I shoot the image."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559000,"text":"Now it's all done on my iPhone,"},{"time":561000,"text":"and it all goes straight up to my server,"},{"time":563000,"text":"and my server does all the backend work"},{"time":565000,"text":"and categorizes things and puts everything together."},{"time":568000,"text":"They need to know where I'm doing my business,"},{"time":570000,"text":"because they want to know about my business."},{"time":573000,"text":"So on December 4th, I went here."},{"time":576000,"text":"And on Sunday, June 14th at 2009 --"},{"time":579000,"text":"this was actually about two o'clock in the afternoon"},{"time":581000,"text":"in Skowhegan, Maine -- this was my apartment there."},{"time":583000,"text":"So what you're basically seeing here"},{"time":586000,"text":"is all bits and pieces and all this information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588000,"text":"If you go to my site, there's tons of things."},{"time":591000,"text":"And really, it's not the most user-friendly interface."},{"time":594000,"text":"It's actually quite user-unfriendly."},{"time":598000,"text":"And one of the reasons, also being part of the user-unfriendliness,"},{"time":600000,"text":"is that everything is there,"},{"time":602000,"text":"but you have to really work through it."},{"time":604000,"text":"So by me putting all this information out there,"},{"time":608000,"text":"what I'm basically telling you is I'm telling you everything."},{"time":611000,"text":"But in this barrage of noise"},{"time":613000,"text":"that I'm putting out,"},{"time":615000,"text":"I actually live an incredibly anonymous and private life."},{"time":619000,"text":"And you know very little about me actually."},{"time":623000,"text":"And really so I've come to the conclusion"},{"time":626000,"text":"that the way you protect your privacy,"},{"time":628000,"text":"particularly in an era where everything is cataloged"},{"time":630000,"text":"and everything is archived and everything is recorded,"},{"time":632000,"text":"there's no need to delete information anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635000,"text":"So what do you do when everything is out there?"},{"time":638000,"text":"Well you have to take control over it."},{"time":640000,"text":"And if I give you this information directly,"},{"time":643000,"text":"it's a very different type of identity"},{"time":646000,"text":"than if you were to try to go through and try to get bits and pieces."},{"time":649000,"text":"The other thing that's also interesting that's going on here"},{"time":652000,"text":"is the fact that intelligence agencies --"},{"time":654000,"text":"and it doesn't matter who they are --"},{"time":657000,"text":"they all operate in an industry"},{"time":659000,"text":"where their commodity is information,"},{"time":661000,"text":"or restricted access to information."},{"time":663000,"text":"And the reason their information has any value"},{"time":666000,"text":"is, well, because no one else has access to it."},{"time":669000,"text":"And by me cutting out the middle man"},{"time":671000,"text":"and giving it straight to you,"},{"time":674000,"text":"the information that the FBI has has no value,"},{"time":677000,"text":"so thus devaluing their currency."},{"time":680000,"text":"And I understand that, on an individual level,"},{"time":682000,"text":"it's purely symbolic."},{"time":684000,"text":"But if 300 million people in the U.S."},{"time":686000,"text":"started doing this,"},{"time":688000,"text":"we would have to redesign the entire intelligence system"},{"time":690000,"text":"from the ground up."},{"time":692000,"text":"Because it just wouldn't work if everybody was sharing everything."},{"time":695000,"text":"And we're getting to that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":697000,"text":"When I first started this project,"},{"time":699000,"text":"people were looking at me and saying,"},{"time":701000,"text":"\"Why would you want to tell everybody what you're doing, where you're at?"},{"time":704000,"text":"Why are you posting these photos?\""},{"time":706000,"text":"This was an age before people were Tweeting everywhere"},{"time":710000,"text":"and 750 million people"},{"time":713000,"text":"were posting status messages"},{"time":715000,"text":"or poking people."},{"time":717000,"text":"So in a way, I'm glad that I'm completely obsolete."},{"time":720000,"text":"I'm still doing this project, but it is obsolete,"},{"time":723000,"text":"because you're all doing it."},{"time":725000,"text":"This is something that we all are doing on a daily basis,"},{"time":727000,"text":"whether we're aware of it or not."},{"time":729000,"text":"So we're creating our own archives and so on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732000,"text":"And you know, some of my friends have always said,"},{"time":735000,"text":"\"Hey, you're just paranoid. Why are you doing this?"},{"time":737000,"text":"Because no one's really watching."},{"time":739000,"text":"No one's really going to bother you.\""},{"time":741000,"text":"So one of the things that I do"},{"time":743000,"text":"is I actually look through my server logs very carefully."},{"time":745000,"text":"Because it's about surveillance."},{"time":747000,"text":"I'm watching who's watching me."},{"time":750000,"text":"And I came up with these."},{"time":752000,"text":"So these are some of my sample logs."},{"time":754000,"text":"And just little bits and pieces, and you can see some of the things there."},{"time":757000,"text":"And I cleaned up the list a little bit so you can see."},{"time":760000,"text":"So you can see that the Homeland Security likes to come by --"},{"time":763000,"text":"Department of Homeland Security."},{"time":765000,"text":"You can see the National Security Agency likes to come by."},{"time":767000,"text":"I actually moved very close to them. I live right down the street from them now."},{"time":771000,"text":"Central Intelligence Agency."},{"time":773000,"text":"Executive Office of the President."},{"time":777000,"text":"Not really sure why they show up, but they do."},{"time":780000,"text":"I think they kind of like to look at art."},{"time":782000,"text":"And I'm glad that we have patrons of the arts in these fields."}]},{"cues":[{"time":786000,"text":"So thank you very much. I appreciate it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":788000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":798000,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Hasan, just curious."},{"time":800000,"text":"You said, \"Now everything automatically goes from my iPhone,\""},{"time":803000,"text":"but actually you do take the pictures and put on information."},{"time":805000,"text":"So how many hours of the day does that take?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":808000,"text":"HE: Almost none."},{"time":810000,"text":"It's no different"},{"time":812000,"text":"than sending a text."},{"time":814000,"text":"It's no different than checking an email."},{"time":817000,"text":"It's one of those things, we got by just fine before we had to do any of those."},{"time":819000,"text":"So it's just become another day."},{"time":821000,"text":"I mean, when we update a status message,"},{"time":823000,"text":"we don't really think about how long that's going to take."},{"time":826000,"text":"So it's really just a matter of my phone clicking a couple of clicks,"},{"time":828000,"text":"send, and then it's done."},{"time":830000,"text":"And everything's automated at the other end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832000,"text":"BG: On the day you are in a place where there is no coverage, the FBI gets crazy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":835000,"text":"HE: Well it goes to the last point that I was at."},{"time":837000,"text":"So it holds onto the very last point."},{"time":839000,"text":"So if I'm on a 12-hour flight,"},{"time":841000,"text":"you'll see the last airport that I departed from."}]},{"cues":[{"time":844000,"text":"BG: Hasan, thank you very much. (HE: Thank you.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":847000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}